165
00:07:46,720 --> 00:07:48,519
He needs time to accept new things.

166
00:07:48,519 --> 00:07:49,600
It's a process.

167
00:07:57,120 --> 00:07:57,839
Put your mask on.

168
00:08:03,879 --> 00:08:04,480
It's fine.

169
00:08:04,959 --> 00:08:06,720
I'll check on Murat's Dad in the backyard.

170
00:08:08,519 --> 00:08:10,040
