173
00:08:48,919 --> 00:08:50,519
Dressed so well,

174
00:08:51,159 --> 00:08:52,960
never orders a single dish.

175
00:08:53,360 --> 00:08:55,559
Goes straight to our free pilaf spot.

176
00:08:56,360 --> 00:08:58,039
Eats happily every time.

177
00:08:59,039 --> 00:09:00,399
I think he comes here

178
