Every family has its own troubles.

189
00:09:20,840 --> 00:09:22,919
Running a restaurant isn't just for money.

190
00:09:38,399 --> 00:09:39,159
Sorry about that.

191
00:09:39,159 --> 00:09:39,639
We...

192
00:09:41,840 --> 00:09:42,519
You're here.

193
00:09:42,799 --> 00:09:43,639
Just got off work?

194
00:09:43,720 --> 00:09:44,399
Have you eaten?

195
00:09:44,399 --> 00:09:45,320
I'll make you something to eat.

196
00:09:45,320 --> 00:09:46,200
No, no, it's fine.

197
00:09:47,320 --> 00:09:48,360
I need to borrow your jacket.

198
00:09:50,080 --> 00:09:50,840
My jacket?

199
00:09:51,279 --> 00:09:52,159
It's not for me.

200
00:09:52,759 --> 00:09:53,840
It's for Smiley, the little brown bear.

201
00:09:59,320 --> 00:10:01,399
