204
00:10:05,960 --> 00:10:07,440
It means I'm still useful to you.

205
00:10:08,840 --> 00:10:10,960
You've been helping me a lot lately.

206
00:10:11,559 --> 00:10:12,200
Finally,

207
00:10:12,799 --> 00:10:14,480
