208
00:10:15,159 --> 00:10:16,720
You've helped me plenty too.

209
00:10:21,159 --> 00:10:22,279
With lots of things.

210
00:10:23,720 --> 00:10:24,519
Even if you talk about it,

211
00:10:24,519 --> 00:10:25,960
