228
00:11:06,720 --> 00:11:08,159
See if your jacket helps.

229
00:11:08,320 --> 00:11:09,159
If you need anything,

230
00:11:09,639 --> 00:11:10,919
I'll always be here to help.

231
00:11:11,919 --> 00:11:12,440
Okay.

232
00:11:13,639 --> 00:11:14,159
I'm heading out.

233
00:11:14,440 --> 00:11:14,919
