248
00:12:16,799 --> 00:12:17,399
What's wrong?

249
00:12:28,879 --> 00:12:29,519
It's fine, it's fine.

250
00:12:30,120 --> 00:12:31,039
It's nothing serious.

251
00:12:31,519 --> 00:12:32,080
Look.

252
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,799
